        <mxCell id="hw-note-sw" value="软件栈&#xa;&#xa;Driver: NVIDIA 580.105.08&#xa;CUDA: 13.0&#xa;Python: 3.12&#xa;PyTorch: + Gloo/NCCL&#xa;NVSHMEM: nvidia-nvshmem-cu12 &gt;= 3.3.9&#xa;nvshmem4py: nvshmem4py-cu12 &gt;= 0.1.2&#xa;Triton-distributed: backends nvidia,amd,proton,distributed&#xa;Bonding driver: v5.15.0" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#666666;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=10;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="60" y="1010" width="500" height="210" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="hw-note-perf" value="性能关键点 &amp; 注意事项&#xa;&#xa;1. NVLink 5 NV18: ~900 GB/s 单向/GPU对, 全 mesh&#xa;2. PCIe Gen5 x16: ~64 GB/s 双向 (GPU&lt;-&gt;NIC)&#xa;3. GPU-NIC PIX 直连: GPUDirect RDMA 最优路径&#xa;4. 跨 NUMA (SYS): GPU0-3 访问 NIC4-7 需跨 UPI, 延迟高&#xa;5. NVSHMEM bootstrap: IFNAME=bond0 (非 eth0!)&#xa;6. NCCL: NCCL_SOCKET_IFNAME=bond0&#xa;7. torchrun: rdzv_endpoint=10.77.188.34:23456&#xa;8. 所有物理NIC MTU=9000 (Jumbo Frames)" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=10;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="580" y="1010" width="520" height="210" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="hw-note-map" value="nvidia-smi topo -m 实测 NIC# 对照 (13 个 NIC 标号)&#xa;━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━&#xa;NIC0  = mlx5_0     = ens123np0 = 18:00.0 GPU0 PIX 400GbE RoCE&#xa;NIC1  = mlx5_1     = ibs20f0   = 2D:00.0 IB HDR100  ┐&#xa;NIC2  = mlx5_2     = ibs20f1   = 2D:00.1 IB HDR100  ├ 同 1 张&#xa;NIC3  = mlx5_3     = ibs20f2   = 2D:00.2 IB HDR100  │ CX-7 卡&#xa;NIC4  = mlx5_4     = ibs20f3   = 2D:00.3 IB HDR100  ┘ (4 端口)&#xa;NIC5  = mlx5_5     = ens122np0 = 3E:00.0 GPU1 PIX 400GbE RoCE&#xa;NIC6  = mlx5_8     = ens121np0 = 5F:00.0 GPU2 PIX 400GbE RoCE&#xa;NIC7  = mlx5_9     = ens120np0 = 71:00.0 GPU3 PIX 400GbE RoCE&#xa;NIC8  = mlx5_10    = ens116np0 = 97:00.0 GPU4 PIX 400GbE RoCE&#xa;NIC9  = mlx5_11    = ens117np0 = BA:00.0 GPU5 PIX 400GbE RoCE&#xa;NIC10 = mlx5_12    = ens118np0 = DC:00.0 GPU6 PIX 400GbE RoCE&#xa;NIC11 = mlx5_13    = ens119np0 = EE:00.0 GPU7 PIX 400GbE RoCE&#xa;NIC12 = mlx5_bond_0 = bond0    = 4C:00.x CX-6 Dx 前向管理&#xa;⚠ mlx5_6/_7 (eth2/eth3) 被 bond 吸收, ibstat 不单独显示&#xa;⚠ NIC# 跳号: 1-4 是 IB, 5-11 才是 GPU PIX 后向 RoCE" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=9;fontFamily=Courier New;align=left;spacingLeft=10;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1120" y="1010" width="520" height="210" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="hw-note-warn" value="网卡编号陷阱&#xa;&#xa;ens 编号和 NIC# 不是顺序对应!&#xa;NIC0 (GPU0) 实际是 ens123np0 (不是 ens116np0)&#xa;mlx5 设备编号按 PCI 枚举顺序, 不按 GPU 顺序&#xa;&#xa;NVSHMEM_BOOTSTRAP_UID_SOCK_IFNAME&#xa;默认 eth0 在此机器上不存在&#xa;必须改为 bond0 (IP: 10.77.188.34)&#xa;并设置 NVSHMEM_BOOTSTRAP_UID_SOCK_FAMILY=AF_INET" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=10;fontStyle=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1660" y="1010" width="490" height="210" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="hw-legend-title" value="图例" style="text;html=1;fontSize=13;fontStyle=1;fillColor=none;strokeColor=none;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="2170" y="1010" width="60" height="20" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="hw-leg1" value="" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#666666;strokeColor=#333333;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="2170" y="1040" width="30" height="15" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="hw-leg1t" value="GPU (B200)" style="text;html=1;fontSize=10;fillColor=none;strokeColor=none;" parent="1" vertex="1">
